com.google.flightmap.db
Class JdbcAviationDbAdapter

java.lang.Object
  com.google.flightmap.db.JdbcAviationDbAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
AviationDbAdapter, DbAdapter, AviationDbReader
public class JdbcAviationDbAdapter
extends Object
implements AviationDbAdapter, AviationDbReader

JDBC adapter for aviation database This adapted is NOT meant to be used in production environment, as it is neither optimized nor thread-safe. It is rather intended to be used during preprocessing, mainly to populate the aviation database.

APPROXIMATE_AIRPORT_COUNT

private static final int APPROXIMATE_AIRPORT_COUNT
Approximate number of airports in db. The accuracy of this value is not critical: it is only Used for optimization reasons (for instance, to initialize collections such as ArrayLists).
